	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />fixed it! in case anybody else runs into this problem, these games were writing palette indexes greater than 63 into the palette RAM. when rendering, i have it AND the palette index with $7F. looks perfect.
<br />
<br /><img src="http://rubbermallet.org/moarnes-punchout-bg-fixed.png" alt="Image" />

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


